item.title: First baseball game ever at Yankees Stadium, Bronx - Yankees vs. Orioles
item.description: First baseball game ever! Pictures from the Yankees Stadium, Bronx - Yankees vs. Orioles. Unfortunately Orioles lost that game on Saturday. They won the game on Sunday 5-2.
